<item>
            <title>[OAK-2420] DocumentNodeStore revision GC may lead to NPE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2420</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The DocumentNodeStore revision GC may cause a NPE in a reader thread when the GC deletes documents currently accessed by the reader. The &lt;tt&gt;docChildrenCache&lt;/tt&gt; is invalidated in &lt;tt&gt;VersionGarbageCollector.collectDeletedDocuments()&lt;/tt&gt; after documents are removed in the DocumentStore. The NPE may occur if removed documents are access in between.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
